American Express Overseas Credit Corp isissuing a 50 mln New Zealand dlr bond due April 27, 1990carrying a coupon of 18 pct and priced at 101-1/4, said HambrosBank Ltd as lead manager.    The issue is guaranteed by American Express Co. Payment isset for April 27, 1987 and the securities will be listed on theLuxembourg stock exchange.    There is a one pct selling concession and a 1/2 pctcombined underwriting and management fee. REUTER&#3;